snippet.title: Early trailer for the game "My Child: Lebensborn", now on Kickstarter
snippet.description:
An early trailer for the mobile game "My Child: Lebensborn" – a story-driven nurture game based on true events. (no sound).

Now on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1071941972/my-child-lebensborn-a-nurture-game-about-emotional?ref=63lvrf
